@node "ab2" "Tutor, about tutor files"
@{b}----------------------------------------------------------------------------
                          Music File System Tutor
                       (c)95/96/97/98   R.F.Bisschop
----------------------------------------------------------------------------@{ub}

I included 3 tutor files you can fool around with.
2 .MFS files (normal projects)  and 1 .MFL (Mutli project) file.

The two MFS files have some CD's and Tapes of my own collection.
 -Tutor01.MFS & Tutor02.MFS
The MFL consists of the 2 MFS files.
 -TutorMFL.MFL

To open a MFS file select Menubar/Project/Project open
To open a MFL file select Menubar/Project/Multi open
You might have to use Menubar/Project/Multifile or Single file, to 
switch to different file mode, before you can select '... open'.
@endnode
